---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'May 2025';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="Amplifly terms of service."
>
  <main class="container mx-auto px-6 pt-32 pb-20 max-w-3xl">

    <h1 class="text-deep-navy text-4xl font-bold mb-3">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="text-neutral-gray text-sm mb-12">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

    <div class="space-y-10 text-accessible-gray text-base leading-relaxed">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-deep-navy text-2xl font-bold mb-4">1. Acceptance</h2>
        <p>
          By downloading or using Amplifly, you agree to these Terms of Service. If you do not
          agree, do not use the app.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-deep-navy text-2xl font-bold mb-4">2. What Amplifly is</h2>
        <p>
          Amplifly is a personal productivity and self-understanding tool designed for
          neurodivergent individuals. It is <strong>not a medical device</strong> and is not
          intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any condition. Nothing in Amplifly
          constitutes medical advice. Always consult a qualified healthcare professional for
          any health-related questions or decisions.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-deep-navy text-2xl font-bold mb-4">3. Your account</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Creating an account is optional. If you create one, you are responsible for
          maintaining the security of your credentials. Notify us immediately at{' '}
          <a href="mailto:hello@amplifly.app" class="text-bright-blue hover:underline">hello@amplifly.app</a>{' '}
          if you suspect unauthorized access.
        </p>
        <p>
          You may delete your account at any time by emailing us. We will remove all associated
          data from Supabase within 7 days of your request.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-deep-navy text-2xl font-bold mb-4">4. Pricing</h2>
        <p>
          Amplifly is currently free to download and use. All core features — brain check-ins,
          conditions, flow logging, the recommender, and the operating manual — are available
          without payment. Creating an account for cross-device sync is also free.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4">
          If we introduce paid features in the future, we will provide clear notice in advance
          and obtain your explicit consent before any charges.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-deep-navy text-2xl font-bold mb-4">5. User responsibilities</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Use Amplifly only for lawful personal purposes.</li>
          <li>Do not attempt to reverse engineer, decompile, or tamper with the app.</li>
          <li>Do not attempt to gain unauthorized access to any backend infrastructure.</li>
          <li>You are responsible for the content you enter (notes, activity descriptions, etc.).</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-deep-navy text-2xl font-bold mb-4">6. Intellectual property</h2>
        <p>
          All app code, design, copy, and algorithms are owned by Amplifly. Your personal data
          (check-ins, sessions, profile) belongs to you. We claim no ownership over the content
          you create within the app.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-deep-navy text-2xl font-bold mb-4">7. Disclaimer of warranties</h2>
        <p>
          Amplifly is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind, express or implied.
          We do not warrant that the app will be uninterrupted, error-free, or that any
          recommendation will produce a particular outcome.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-deep-navy text-2xl font-bold mb-4">8. Limitation of liability</h2>
        <p>
          To the maximum extent permitted by law, Amplifly and its founders shall not be
          liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use
          of the app.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-deep-navy text-2xl font-bold mb-4">9. Changes to these terms</h2>
        <p>
          We may update these terms from time to time. Material changes will be communicated
          via in-app notice. Continued use of Amplifly after changes constitutes acceptance.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-deep-navy text-2xl font-bold mb-4">10. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions about these terms?{' '}
          <a href="mailto:hello@amplifly.app" class="text-bright-blue hover:underline">hello@amplifly.app</a>
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
